quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,52,"Then after that We forgave you so that you might be grateful."
  2,53,"And (remember) when We gave Mûsâ (Moses) the Scripture [the Taurât (Torah)] and the criterion (of right and wrong) so that you may be guided aright."
  2,54,"And (remember) when Mûsâ (Moses) said to his people: "